{"tid":1386601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[改寫命運]  8.5大罷工","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:46:13.000Z","uid":195252,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"416c599deb934e8e005dc2a43824506ed77fe086","tid":1386601,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"首先，希望民陣既朋友睇到呢個post，幫手呼籲市民參與罷工。因為民陣有號召力，前兩次百萬遊行，就係好好既例子。<br />\n<br />\n第二，見唔到有熱門post講緊8.5大罷工。呢個時候應該集中推8.5大罷工既post，做大個氣勢，；更加多人知，就有更加多人參加。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">麻煩各位巴絲儘量推8.5大罷工既post上去。</span>"},{"pid":"44aa570e0810c43e3d6093193f30fce65f523a2d","tid":1386601,"uid":195252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51QOOhr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51QOOhr.png&h=59a8b083&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e43019bb650072cc8f3cc6f696397ef7af5de21","tid":1386601,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"借個靚位，入黎睇下有冇得搞thx<br />\n<br />\n[歡迎討論] 搵公司幫手推動罷工  入黎討論/屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386150</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9030bb7899010f63ce82f4c58f2cd8bb46e7c2f5","tid":1386601,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fe940c48bada4925495baa80edc7ceb522d6196","tid":1386601,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"大家真係要冷靜， 點解呢一刻出水炮車<br />\n就係因為控告45名義士激起你地怒火<br />\n大家真係唔好俾佢激到， 一定要冷靜<br />\n我地唔可以再有義士犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d43058e5d1c326cab65992d8ec9619fb5c7ee86","tid":1386601,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"如果8.5大罷工空前成功，就會改寫命運，香港人加油<img